Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了將翻過去的單位給抬起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.97,0:01:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們借用了西伯利亞鐵路總帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.84,0:01:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫契茲之人他專用列車的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.18,0:01:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然追著肯恩的人沒有出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.18,0:01:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個工作實在是很費事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.45,0:01:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為莎拉她們也出了相當的力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.39,0:01:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以亞邦居住區的行進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.33,0:01:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又再度恢復朝向東邊而去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.47,0:02:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「地獄的接力賽」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要一口氣做個了斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.71,0:02:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這大將想去哪呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.82,0:02:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標只要鎖定剪影引擎就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.77,0:02:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mach Band！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.21,0:02:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mach Band Shaker啟動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股震動是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.25,0:02:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,札基那傢伙竟敢得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.73,0:03:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是中了「安得葛雷姆」的\NMach Band Shaker
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.43,0:03:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼剪影引擎根本就不堪一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Overman竟然連這種事也要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.75,0:03:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子不都被人看光了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.90,0:03:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉不管做什麼都很棒呀\N我愛你~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.80,0:03:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高烏力隊被打倒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.34,0:03:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，班薩有三台\N分別是重度及中度損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.61,0:03:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊員們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.01,0:03:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以高烏力隊長為首\N所有人都回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.61,0:03:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之後我們非\N越過西伯利亞鐵路不可呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說人手...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想動手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰怕誰呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢這麼說\N你這贊成派的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.33,0:04:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就只會說些膽小的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走就代表有勇氣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要動手的話\N就在運動會的比賽上干啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要瞧不起人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀！上呀上呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好玩呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.71,0:04:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據謠言指出紅隊好像是\N贊成脫逃的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪麼白隊就是反對派了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.95,0:04:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在比賽前就發洩起來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動會果然還是不能中止的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就幫你打點滴\N等等呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你的腦漿沒有爆出來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是受點輕傷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就不用擔心了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我幫你看看呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你能幫我變聰明的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！這有根白頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有白頭髮嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我腦子裡還在搖動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說那招是\NMach Band Shaker是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，好像就是那道光的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛雷姆機種裡有這種傢伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們需要的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.52,0:05:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩台一起攻過來了耶\N還是左右散開突然攻過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.32,0:05:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的戰法都是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，年青人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你來甲板一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它好像要出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也想去運動會呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們前進的方向\N如果保持不變繼續前進下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.27,0:05:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會需要橫跨西伯利亞鐵路\N的線路不可喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們打從一開始就打算這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們要不要利用\N運動會喧鬧的氣氛作為掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.21,0:05:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁機打倒保護線路的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法這麼會改變這麼多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我厭煩了光只是抱怨而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點，不要拖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.59,0:05:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽到了嗎\N凱吉南.恩給！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.23,0:05:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非聽聖雷根\N那群人的命令呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.17,0:05:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在先忍耐一下吧\N只有「現在」喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只有現在而已嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.80,0:06:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們要你們採用\N倫敦派的戰法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把這兩台「安得葛雷姆」\N借給你們的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.58,0:06:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了表示我們的謝意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.59,0:06:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會用London IMA的戰法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.60,0:06:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把「黑色南十字星」給抓來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.77,0:06:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，就是這股幹勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙貝~仙貝~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.00,0:06:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久沒看過學校的競技賽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.28,0:06:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.12,0:06:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些正在脫逃的皮普魯\N到底在辦什麼祭典呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是熱鬧呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.09,0:06:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個承包人說這種事情對\N皮普魯的精神健康很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.69,0:06:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我瞭解他的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有這樣\N可是無法脫逃成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅隊贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在比賽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主，我們有位置可以坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.39,0:07:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來防衛線的部隊\N就部署完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你已經瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.82,0:07:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快點開始行動吧\N只有防守是無法阻止他們脫逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.78,0:07:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是札基送來的指示\N他說確認了敵人的剪影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎後，就開始執行作戰行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.59,0:08:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像笨蛋一樣\N竟然說這種廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.66,0:08:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這個作戰就是\N要把我們用完就丟就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.37,0:08:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度我也能瞭解呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯恩還有蓋那竟然搭檔參賽耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們什麼時候變得那麼意氣\N相投了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.32,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是琉波芙小姐嗎\N我們有幫你們兩位預留了位置喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.29,0:08:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...其實我是想問你們\N你們這邊有沒有看到公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要拿下第一名喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅隊包辦了1.2名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.64,0:08:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋那！接力賽要怎麼辦呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.74,0:08:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給貝洛還有莎拉你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.25,0:08:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在單位跟單位間\N為了接力賽而搭的橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.38,0:09:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經準備妥當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎，加哈大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋的準備已經沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.46,0:09:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看起來像是\N又不堅固又便宜的吊橋就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.09,0:09:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會有20或30個人\N同時過橋的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.73,0:09:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KING-GAINER所拿的東西\N將會變成折返點的指標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那字不會只是\N隨便寫寫的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.52,0:09:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用大家在運動會上\N氣氛炒得熱勝勝的空檔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把高度降低點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要做到\N「請敵人發現我」的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.03,0:09:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一件事想問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.73,0:09:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說如果我們的對手是\N阿斯哈姆的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.97,0:09:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就會中了我們的引誘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.27,0:09:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那麼瞭解阿斯哈姆\N這個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.31,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他的關係可是\N連超逼真的假決鬥都進行過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.14,0:10:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決鬥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.98,0:10:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才想抓我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我們要利用這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用一台就攻了過來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它包圍起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N你們就這麼跟過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.87,0:10:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個動作...\N看起來很像是在引誘我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.47,0:10:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不可以中了他的誘敵之計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪\N他們沒有中計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再試一次，蓋那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.81,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們趕出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道西伯利亞鐵路的人\N也會動腦筋嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體齊射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.57,0:11:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是Overman也好\N想要用一台就衝進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也未免想得太一廂情願了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會派這種伏兵呀\N阿斯哈姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「黑色南十字星」？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是從哪裡攻擊過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.43,0:11:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂！你的如意算盤只打到\N這裡而已嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦，已經要逃了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.12,0:11:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你等好久了\NOverman！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.73,0:12:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的震動\NKING-GAINER才不會放...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.91,0:12:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是安得葛雷姆的\NMach Band Shaker
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你體會一下我們的恨意！\N亞邦的Overman！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人去戰鬥了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.95,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆人目前正在苦戰中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.45,0:13:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是幹掉高烏力隊的\N震動Overman吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬度老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他們會在這種時候\N出擊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去令班薩隊出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派楠和度恩去支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.87,0:13:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉我希望能請你擔任\N紅隊的最後一棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.90,0:13:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是出擊而是要我擔任\N接力賽的最後一棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的情況比較緊急呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.41,0:13:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼呀\N快點開始啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不快點開始\N就要剛剛的互毆秀再上演一次啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.92,0:13:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比較想看人互歐~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是公主嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人質竟然一個人落單\N這樣好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有是事要拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.89,0:13:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得您看起來\N實在是非常「自由」的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.10,0:13:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.77,0:13:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個交給在\N「烏魯古魯斯」的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.93,0:13:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然是自由沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.04,0:13:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你認為我會回\N「烏魯古魯斯」去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.54,0:13:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該會回去吧\N你就是這樣的人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是聰明人該說的話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.28,0:14:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我相當受到你的信任呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.35,0:14:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點也沒有反省\N又想跑來綁架公主的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不錯呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就可以再回警備隊去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.06,0:14:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快離開公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個小姐在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉波芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這種地方幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不阻止那兩個人好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.38,0:14:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬度先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.82,0:14:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正全身麻木顫抖著呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也可以扮演這種腳色啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.40,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.67,0:14:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們完全不知道「黑色南十字星」\N的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.90,0:14:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是他們得意忘形使用了\N那種Over Ski11才會這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.68,0:15:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.91,0:15:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也不要輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.21,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路還遠得很喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要確實把肩帶交給下個人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑在我前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是給我到後面去跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會故意做這種事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個並列了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快給我跌倒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.84,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得要幫反對派\N來跑最後一棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不要你就閉嘴\N趕快滾回去西伯利亞鐵路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司怎麼樣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你沒有自信\N才會說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.92,0:15:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連報個「收下麵包」的恩情\N都不肯呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.82,0:15:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能會輸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.79,0:15:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種比賽的輸贏還是取決\N在「年輕」上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.02,0:15:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這充滿彈性\N又經過千錘百鏈的雙腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.23,0:15:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會輸給一個「小鬼」呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.16,0:15:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐您果然是如我所料\N大有前途的人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.67,0:15:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一開始采這種態度的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.40,0:16:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會更友善的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.74,0:16:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說呀\N在接下肩帶之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好先做好暖身運動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個頑強的Overman
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.45,0:16:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩給\N我們再接近一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他給徹底粉碎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.15,0:16:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要下這種命令\N才像隊長呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.47,0:16:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是「黑色南十字星」的 攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.51,0:16:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.68,0:16:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.15,0:16:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被他們揉得亂七八糟\N連內臟都暴出來了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托此之福讓我知道了\N他們是用兩台Overman
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.92,0:16:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來使用這種Over Ski11
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.92,0:16:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說\N只要打倒一台就行了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.17,0:17:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振動波變成了防護罩\N根本就沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.74,0:17:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先從Overman開始\N給他致命一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一台可以讓我比較確實地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決掉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼震動變弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再更接近一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.44,0:17:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好，你們再接近一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.17,0:17:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再近一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人的話就不能戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐呀~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.75,0:17:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是怎麼回事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要逃啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你們那種Over Ski11的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因為打電動而僵硬的肩膀\N終於治好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震動波無法啟動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.81,0:18:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的蠢蛋們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快往東邊飛過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.18,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令你們引誘他們去\N西伯利亞鐵路的線路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.98,0:18:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要使用「史瓦洛基吉」\N的列車炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.15,0:18:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被阿斯哈姆\N用了這招的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要是不肯幹的話\N我的「強力(Power)葛雷姆」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會把你們給捶爆喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體聽令\N我們退到東方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.83,0:18:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.46,0:18:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算讓他們逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.33,0:18:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算引誘我們去\N鐵路那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.20,0:18:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去追他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要幹件他們最討厭\N的事情...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.30,0:18:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.38,0:19:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是托愛得意忘形的\N凱吉南跟恩給的福...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱吉南，到前面去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是「黑色十字星」的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.16,0:19:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以出手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.93,0:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法呀\NLondon IMA那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不可以殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿斯哈姆那傢伙\N下的命令嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.74,0:19:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然給我坐在列車裡\N真是個懶惰鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們進到射程內了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你開炮打他們不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多可灼隊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那百年如一的老套嗎？\N阿斯哈姆老哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.00,0:19:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線路是要這樣子用的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.98,0:20:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線路被他給...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點阻止他！\N要不然我們會被契茲大人殺掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.93,0:20:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他後退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.86,0:20:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不覺得聖雷根來到這\N西伯利亞很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們最好也快點逃比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要聽你的指使呀\N不要瞧不起人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.14,0:20:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？「史瓦洛基吉」呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢給我來這套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐加油呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的身體已經暖起來了\N所以可以跑得很快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.56,0:20:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教你怎麼訓練的人\N可是我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.40,0:20:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小娃兒\N不要學大人的口氣說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.70,0:21:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.77,0:21:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.94,0:21:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在正在比接力賽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先挑起戰火的人是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.44,0:21:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就救了快要\N餓死的你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.35,0:21:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就這樣凍死也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要說的自己好像是\N恩人一樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.99,0:21:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你胸部大又怎樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個不要輸了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.52,0:21:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的跑者回到第一單位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.46,0:21:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久後她們就要進到\N這個體育館內了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.86,0:21:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情怎麼好像變得很大條了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來\N這還真值得一看呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要輸了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個不相上下呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.38,0:21:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.38,0:21:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個就一起獲得勝利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.48,0:21:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.53,0:22:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.90,0:22:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛...已經夠了，蓋那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.87,0:22:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福，運動會的氣氛\N才能炒得那麼熱呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.20,0:22:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀！皮普魯整體的氣氛好像\N已經沉著下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.57,0:22:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要再幹一次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.34,0:22:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.68,0:22:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了被人強迫以代跑的身份\N下場去比賽之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.81,0:22:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連胸部的大小都輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.78,0:22:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.68,0:22:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.52,0:22:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.82,0:22:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.76,0:22:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.76,0:22:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在開始上課之前\N我要向各位介紹一位新老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.13,0:22:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.10,0:22:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.90,0:22:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.67,0:22:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以變成這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.00,0:22:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋求共存共榮之道\N希望大家可以讓我跟你們學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.64,0:22:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是亞狄特.凱斯拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.28,0:22:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同時也是為了你們大伙\N的為人修養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.58,0:22:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才接受她的要求的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.21,0:22:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教\N小姑娘.小少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.78,0:22:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這種事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.12,0:23:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬度先生他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.71,0:23:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算變成了老師\N人格也不會那麼快就可以改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.64,0:23:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的 OVERMAN KING-GAINER
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.65,0:23:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奮鬥！！亞狄特老師」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.48,0:23:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Hit！
